title: About
text: Hi, I’m Sose and I’m a senior at Penn’s Annenberg School, majoring in Communication with a concentration in data and network science. I also have minors in consumer psychology and history and plan on a career in corporate communications and marketing. I’m excited to show off what I’ve learned in my COMM data and network science classes thus far in the blog posts below!
